00:17:20,100 --> 00:17:22,300
Yep. I slept with him.

295
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:25,066
I slept with him.

296
00:17:25,100 --> 00:17:26,100
He gave me a role.

297
00:17:27,533 --> 00:17:28,533
Fair trade, right?

298
00:17:28,933 --> 00:17:29,933
Yeah.

299
00:17:31,266 --> 00:17:33,366
Guess Fang's gotten bold.

300
00:17:34,433 --> 00:17:35,766
In this industry,

301
00:17:37,266 --> 00:17:38,533
everyone makes sacrifices.

302
00:17:42,666 --> 00:17:45,766
Su Yi got fooled by you.

303
00:17:46,900 --> 00:17:48,200
Told you,

304
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:50,833
he's not worth it. You're more fun.

305
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:56,400
Fancy some wine?

306
00:18:05,433 --> 00:18:06,433
Sure.

307
00:18:21,333 --> 00:18:22,333
Play with me?

308
00:18:29,666 --> 00:18:30,666
Foreplay?

309
00:18:34,233 --> 00:18:35,233
Get lost.

310
00:18:36,833 --> 00:18:38,100
I've seen your type.

311
00:18:39,066 --> 00:18:40,066
You're not worth it.

312
00:18:46,533 --> 00:18:47,533
Pei Jia.

313
00:18:48,266 --> 00:18:49,100
Without the company
and Mr. Fang,

314
00:18:50,300 --> 00:18:51,533
you are nothing!

315
00:19:12,433 --> 00:19:13,300
Exactly.

316
00:19:13,333 --> 00:19:15,200
He kicked me out when I said no.

317
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:17,866
So why did you go to his room?

318
00:19:19,466 --> 00:19:21,133
Director told me to run lines.

319
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:22,600
Should I go now?

320
00:19:23,300 --> 00:19:24,700
No need to bother.

321
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,200
I'll go to set tomorrow.

322
00:19:29,933 --> 00:19:30,933
Alright.

323
00:19:34,200 --> 00:19:35,433
No earpiece today.

324
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:43,333
Shen's entourage is intense.

325
00:19:43,666 --> 00:19:45,766
Three assistants just for a mic.

326
00:19:47,666 --> 00:19:49,499
I'm afraid that someone may hit me

327
00:19:49,500 --> 00:19:50,733
as I refused to be harassed.

328
00:19:53,233 --> 00:19:56,166
Hey, protect Mr. Shen well.

329
00:19:56,466 --> 00:19:58,000
He is a good actor.

330
00:19:59,066 --> 00:20:00,800
Mic him up well.

331
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:03,066
Sound quality matters.

332
00:20:04,533 --> 00:20:05,466
Clear the set.

333
00:20:05,500 --> 00:20:06,933
Ready?

334
00:20:08,033 --> 00:20:10,733
Director, today's scene
is just ambient, no lines.

335
00:20:10,866 --> 00:20:12,966
Then no mics?

336
00:20:13,500 --> 00:20:15,732
Nope, still mic them.

337
00:20:15,733 --> 00:20:17,366
What if they improv?

338
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:18,000
Alright.

339
00:20:18,033 --> 00:20:19,033
Got it.

340
00:20:20,833 --> 00:20:22,233
Move fast.

341
00:20:22,800 --> 00:20:23,800
Mics ready?

342
00:20:24,633 --> 00:20:25,633
Quiet on set!

343
00:20:26,400 --> 00:20:28,233
Scene 12-1, shot 9, take 1.

344
00:20:31,033 --> 00:20:32,033
Okay!

345
00:20:32,800 --> 00:20:33,832
3

346
00:20:33,833 --> 00:20:34,865
2

347
00:20:34,866 --> 00:20:36,000
1

348
00:20:36,033 --> 00:20:37,033
Action.

349
00:20:38,100 --> 00:20:39,100
Stop!

350
00:20:40,733 --> 00:20:42,000
Stop, stop!

351
00:20:42,300 --> 00:20:43,300
Stop!

352
00:20:44,433 --> 00:20:45,433
Cut.

353
00:20:48,500 --> 00:20:49,300
Mr. Fang.

354
00:20:49,333 --> 00:20:50,733
Why do you keep showing up on set?

355
00:20:51,833 --> 00:20:52,866
Others leave.

356
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:54,200
Pei Jia stays.

357
00:20:54,333 --> 00:20:55,732
We're behind schedule,

358
00:20:55,733 --> 00:20:57,633
can we hurry?

359
00:21:02,466 --> 00:21:03,932
Fine, fine.

360
00:21:03,933 --> 00:21:05,566
Everyone's done for the day.

361
00:21:06,266 --> 00:21:07,266
Pei Jia stays.

362
00:21:10,733 --> 00:21:11,866
Obedient now, huh?

363
00:21:33,066 --> 00:21:34,200
Powerful enough

364
00:21:34,733 --> 00:21:37,366
to shut the whole crew down.

365
00:21:38,133 --> 00:21:39,293
What did you do to Shen Xing?

366
00:21:42,500 --> 00:21:44,833
That little pet of yours?

367
00:21:45,700 --> 00:21:47,033
I came here last time

368
00:21:47,466 --> 00:21:50,100
to deal with a pet problem as well.

369
00:21:51,933 --> 00:21:53,033
He can be tamed.

370
00:21:53,500 --> 00:21:54,500
But I can't.

371
00:22:10,633 --> 00:22:12,633
Find out who is the master
before beating the dog.

372
00:22:14,466 --> 00:22:17,899
You didn't come here
just to slap me, right?

373
00:22:17,900 --> 00:22:20,766
Now you realize how
important you are to me?

374
00:22:23,800 --> 00:22:24,800
What about Su Yi?

375
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:25,933
Is he important?
Su Yi?

376
00:22:27,433 --> 00:22:28,966
Your dying little pet?

377
00:22:29,600 --> 00:22:30,600
He's my lover.

378
00:22:31,533 --> 00:22:32,866
Well, he's awfully disobedient.

379
00:22:33,466 --> 00:22:34,366
I warned him

380
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:35,900
not to contact you anymore.

381
00:22:36,666 --> 00:22:37,666
How did you warn him?

382
00:22:38,833 --> 00:22:40,466
You haven't seen those photos.

383
00:22:41,233 --> 00:22:42,433
They're quite something.

384
00:22:42,900 --> 00:22:44,033
Young and wild.

385
00:22:45,933 --> 00:22:47,033
Su Yi's not like that.

386
00:22:48,300 --> 00:22:50,700
Took a lot of drugs

387
00:22:50,866 --> 00:22:52,366
to get him in bed.

388
00:22:53,333 --> 00:22:54,433
You really should see it.

389
00:22:54,466 --> 00:22:56,666
He didn't want it.

390
00:22:57,200 --> 00:22:58,400
It even made me

391
00:22:59,800 --> 00:23:01,600
feel bad for him.

392
00:23:02,600 --> 00:23:03,866
Why did you do it?

393
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:06,533
If you behaved good,

394
00:23:06,933 --> 00:23:08,166
I wouldn't need to drug him.

395
00:23:09,233 --> 00:23:10,833
Though I can't get you,

396
00:23:11,533 --> 00:23:12,933
I'd take your pet.

397
00:23:13,666 --> 00:23:14,766
I'll kill you!

398
00:23:15,066 --> 00:23:16,800
Pei Jia! Pei Jia! Pei Jia!

399
00:23:16,866 --> 00:23:18,100
He just admitted it.

400
00:23:18,233 --> 00:23:18,966
He did.
Calm down.

401
00:23:19,401 --> 00:23:20,665
Admitted? Admitted what?

402
00:23:20,666 --> 00:23:21,733
That I hit you?

403
00:23:21,933 --> 00:23:22,400
Huh?

404
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:24,209
Yi, didn't you say he sucked at acting

405
00:23:24,233 --> 00:23:25,299
and asked me to teach him a lesson?

406
00:23:25,300 --> 00:23:26,300
Right?

407
00:23:27,133 --> 00:23:28,173
This is for your own good.

408
00:23:28,266 --> 00:23:29,626
Mr. Fang doing so is for our sake.

409
00:23:33,100 --> 00:23:34,100
Trust me.

410
00:23:41,033 --> 00:23:42,033
Fine.

411
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:43,200
Got it.
